Project Title	E-commerce Sales Performance & Profitability Dashboard
Submitted By	AVIN

Business Objective
To build an interactive Power BI dashboard that provides actionable insights into sales performance, profit margins, customer behaviour, and regional trends to support data-driven business decisions.
Problem Statement
Business Challenges
E-commerce businesses face difficulty in:
•	Tracking real-time sales performance across categories
•	Understanding profit margins at product level
•	Identifying top-performing regions and customers
•	Measuring impact of discounts on profitability
•	Making data-driven decisions without centralized reporting
Solution
An interactive Power BI dashboard that provides:
•	Centralized view of all key metrics
•	Drill-down capabilities by year, region, and category
•	Visual insights into sales trends and patterns
•	Actionable recommendations for business growth

