Measure Descriptions
Key Insights & Findings

Insight 1: Sales Performance
Finding: Total Sales reached 533.67M, exceeding target by 6.7%.
Impact: Strong overall business performance.
Action: Maintain current sales strategies.

Insight 2: Payment Mode Preference
Finding: Credit Card and UPI are the most used payment methods (combined 60%+).
Impact: Digital payments dominate.
Action: Promote digital payment offers.

Insight 3: Regional Performance
Finding: South region shows highest profit margin.
Impact: Geographic expansion opportunity.
Action: Increase marketing spends in South region.

Insight 4: Product Category Analysis
Finding: Electronics category generates highest sales volume.
Impact: Key revenue driver identified.
Action: Ensure adequate Electronics inventory.

Insight 5: Customer Behaviour
Finding: Top 10 customers contribute significantly to revenue.
Impact: Customer concentration risk.
Action: Launch loyalty program for top customers.

Insight 6: Discount Impact
Finding: Average discount of 10% maintains healthy 14.94% profit margin.
Impact: Current discount strategy is optimal.
Action: Maintain current discount levels.

Business Recommendations
Recommendation 1: Inventory Management
Increase Electronics category inventory - As the highest sales category (533.67M), ensure popular sub-categories are always in stock.
Recommendation 2: Payment Optimization
Promote Credit Card and UPI payments - Offer cashback/discounts for digital payments to reduce COD costs.
Recommendation 3: Regional Expansion
Expand operations in South region - With highest profit margins, open additional fulfilment centres.
Recommendation 4: Customer Loyalty Program
Launch loyalty program for top 10 customers - Retain high-value customers with exclusive benefits.
Recommendation 5: Discount Strategy
Maintain 10% average discount - Current discount level optimizes both sales volume and profit margin.
Recommendation 6: Seasonal Planning
Prepare for Q4 sales increase - Based on monthly trends, increase inventory and marketing in Oct-Dec.



